<L>__{interior great jones st. loft day}
<A>__{washed in sunlight, a large painting leans against the wall, the words "haitian baseball factories" scrawled through its center. jean lays down, watching tv. he looks older now, more worn. his face is slightly swollen. his complexion is discolored. shenge covers a triptych with wide brush strokes of yellow painterior he circles a large, primitive figure of a black man drawn with magic marker in the center. he is careful to leave the figure intact.}
