<D>__{wanna bet? if you show too much respect for people with money, they don't have respect for you.}
<A>__{maria, a raven haired, sharp featured beauty in a chanel suit jacket, blue jeans, and pearls walks into the room. she's with ellen younger a millionaire fake hippie from texas. maria carries a bag with clogs in it a present for jean. she takes them out.}
